| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1164 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0684e38e-b8a1-53eb-b5db-e17f6c189ace"
